DELFASCO, LLC, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
GTI SYSTEMS, INC., Mark Benko and Stephen Powell, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D18-2998 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. October 11, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

Appellees' motions to dismiss is granted, and this appeal is dismissed. Appellant's motion for an extension of time is denied as moot.

CRENSHAW, BLACK, and BADALAMENTI, JJ., Concur.
